---
const props = Astro.props;

import ImageCard from '../../ImageCard.astro';
import icon from '../../../assets/inventory/sword/Nocturnal Glow.png'
---

<ImageCard image={icon} title="Nocturnal Glow">
<p>Increases ATK and DEF by <span class="text-orange-500">4</span>-<span class="text-orange-500">10%</span>. After the character casts a skill on allies, additionally dispels <span class="text-orange-500">1</span>-<span class="text-orange-500">2</span> [debuff] from them and grants <span class="text-orange-500">1</span> random [<span class="text-yellow-500">Level 1 Buff</span>]-[<span class="text-yellow-500">Level 2 Buff</span>] and [<span class="text-yellow-500">Nocturnal Glow I</span>]-[<span class="text-yellow-500">Nocturnal Glow II</span>] for <span class="text-orange-500">2</span> turns.</p>
</ImageCard>
